snippet.title: Omega Royale Alpha Event | Winner Replay
snippet.description:
The first ever launch of Omega Royale Alpha was a success, thanks to our community! The launch happened June 29, 2022 and lasted for two weeks.

This is a replay of the winning game by Bamboocha. The end score was an insane 6 804! Maybe this video will reveal some secrets to how the highest score was achieved...

If you’d like to get the latest of what we’re working on, be sure to follow our channels:

Discord: https://discord.gg/RN9u2zvHRa
Twitter: https://twitter.com/OmegaRoyaleEN
Website: https://omegaroyale.com
